џOur fondest memories of
Darren Evans
"Daz"
From your lifelong friends & family
x x x

Behind our smiles are many a tear,
For you Daz, who we loved & lost so dear.
An empty place that can't be filled,
We miss you now and always will.
We sit here with you for a while,
Remembering your energy & your smile.
At this special place our hearts are with you,
As we remember "Happy Days" & enjoy the view."е
